    "Name": "Dominatrix DTX-96",
    "Details": "The DTX-96 is a unique Solaris VII gladiatorial machine commissioned by Canopian noblewoman Anya Sokolov. MASC pushes the 55-ton frame to 129 kph in short bursts, closing distance before opponents can react. A Chain Whip and Vibroblade handle melee while Spikes punish anything that strikes back. Twin Medium VSP Lasers and a Small VSP Laser reward the close range the design constantly demands, and a hidden Flamer in the center torso adds one final unpleasant surprise.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Melee Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
